
 Sony driver changes:

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1.00    11-May-93      First version of this soft-loadable CD-ROM driver.
                        Includes 6XXX, 541 and 561 support (561 supports mode 1 and mode2 form 1)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1.01    07-Jul-93      - Extended for 561 to include support for mode 2 discs, ie. now supports
                        mode 1, mode 2 form 1, and mode 2.
                        - kludge added for mode 2 form 1 discs so that the end of the disc can
                        be read !! - need to set the drives buffer size to 1 block.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1.02    15-Sep-93      - CD_PlayTrack for 561 drive did not play one track properly.
                        - CD_PlayTrack r6 was not cleared before being used.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1.03    18-Oct-93      - Support added for SONY 561 drive to read multi-session discs
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1.04    25-Oct-93      - Support for single session PhotoCD for Sony 541 drives
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1.05    03-Nov-93      - SetParameters changed so that only send it if User needs to change
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1.06    05-Jul-94      - CD_ReadAudio added
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
